<div class="content">
  <div class="left-block">
    <div class="comment-form">
      <h2>Vent Away!</h2>
      <%= render "form", comment: comment %>
    </div>
    <div>
      <h2>Vents:</h2>
      <% if comments.blank? %>
        <p>No on has vented yet today. Be the first!</p>
      <% end %>
      <ul class="comment-index">
        <% comments.each do |comment| %>
          <li class="comment">
            <p><%= comment.text %></p>
            <sub class="published">Submitted <%= submit_time(comment) %> ago.</sub>
          </li>
        <% end %>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="right-block">
    <h2>Welcome to Venter</h2>
    <p id="toggle" class="toggle">Instructions<i class="fa fa-chevron-down" aria-hidden="true"></i></p>
    <span id="instructions" class="instructions"><p>Need to get something off your chest but don't want anyone to know you said it? Well, now's your chance! Leave an angry comment, a confession of love, or absolute gibberish--it's your choice, and it's all anonymous! We clear the board daily so that no baggage you drop off here finds you again.</p></span>
  </div>
</div>
